  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Problem\r\n\r\nSometimes app crashes after tapping + > start new chat (e2e tests caught this behavior 2 times in one set of 150 e2e).\r\nCouldn't reproduce manually.\r\nMost likely was introduced by https://github.com/status-im/status-react/pull/9571, was found during testing rebased https://github.com/status-im/status-react/pull/9547\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nno crash\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\napp crashed\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Restore multiaccount from seed phrase\r\n- Tap on + > New chat\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: develop after https://github.com/status-im/status-react/pull/9571\r\n- Operating System: so far Android\r\n\r\n#### Logs\r\n\r\nFull video / logcat is [here](https://app.saucelabs.com/tests/43527423de714648881de6508cbf82b4?auth=e3f92a1ede922c99b2b49273fe05fa0d)\r\n\r\nCrash logs:\r\n```\r\n12-04 07:05:33.317  4351  4377 D ReactNativeJS: DEBUG [status-im.ui.screens.routing.core:34] - :on-will-focus :new-chat\r\n12-04 07:05:33.323  4351  4351 E JavaBinder: !!! FAILED BINDER TRANSACTION !!!  (parcel size = 448)\r\n12-04 07:05:33.323  4351  4351 D AndroidRuntime: Shutting down VM\r\n12-04 07:05:33.324  1636  1704 W InputDispatcher: channel '264c501 im.status.ethereum.pr/im.status.ethereum.MainActivity (server)' ~ Consumer closed input channel or an error occurred.  events=0x9\r\n12-04 07:05:33.324  1636  1704 E InputDispatcher: channel '264c501 im.status.ethereum.pr/im.status.ethereum.MainActivity (server)' ~ Channel is unrecoverably broken and will be disposed!\r\n--------- beginning of crash\r\n12-04 07:05:33.324  4351  4351 E AndroidRuntime: FATAL EXCEPTION: main\r\n12-04 07:05:33.324  4351  4351 E AndroidRuntime: Process: im.status.ethereum.pr, PID: 4351\r\n12-04 07:05:33.324  4351  4351 E AndroidRuntime: java.lang.RuntimeException: Adding window failed\r\n12-04 07:05:33.324  4351  4351 E AndroidRuntime:  at android.view.ViewRootImpl.setView(ViewRootImpl.java:738)\r\n12-04 07:05:33.324  4351  4351 E AndroidRuntime:  at android.view.WindowManagerGlobal.addView(WindowManagerGlobal.java:356)\r\n12-04 07:05:33.324  4351  4351 E AndroidRuntime:  at android.view.WindowManagerImpl.addView(WindowManagerImpl.java:92)\r\n12-04 07:05:33.324  4351  4351 E AndroidRuntime:  at android.app.Dialog.show(Dialog.java:330)\r\n```",
